26
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:10,630
Running
an Errand

27
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:09,360
Running an errand!

28
00:01:19,970 --> 00:01:25,020
Nohara

29
00:01:19,970 --> 00:01:25,020
Hiroshi
Misae
Shinnosuke

30
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:30,900
Oh no! I forgot to buy the ground pork and radishes!

31
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,920
Now I've done it.

32
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:39,080
We're out of soy sauce too!

33
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:41,580
Shoot! And I have my hands full at the moment.

34
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:44,120
What should I do?

35
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,300
Oh, I know!
I'll get Shinnosuke to go for me.

36
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:50,050
He's never gone shopping by himself before,

37
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,539
so it'll be a good
experience for him.

38
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,740
Shinnosuke!

39
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:54,940
What?

40
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,720
Can you come here for a sec?

41
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,970
I can't right now. I'm drawing!

42
00:01:58,970 --> 00:02:02,970
What a defiant brat. I suppose I'll have to soft-soap him.

43
00:02:02,970 --> 00:02:05,200
Did it turn out nice?

44
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,000
Yeah!

45
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,440
I want to see it!

46
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,139
Sure!

47
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:15,280
Check it out. It's an elephant!

48
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:19,360
An elephant, an elephant...

49
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:22,100
He's such a fool.

50
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:24,829
I don't have time for this!

51
00:02:24,829 --> 00:02:28,660
And Mom... and Dad...

52
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:32,250
Listen to me!
Put on some underwear!

53
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:37,240
I put on some underwear. What did you want?

54
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,720
Go shopping for me.

55
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:42,200
Do it yourself, Misae.

56
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:45,890
How many times have I told you not to imitate your father?

57
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:47,350
I know, Misae.

58
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:51,280
Don't call your
parents by their names.

59
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,320
Yes, ma'am.

60
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:55,840
Tonight, your father is bringing home a very important client,

61
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,700
so I'm making a special dinner.

62
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,600
I see.

63
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:01,280
That's why I'm so busy.

64
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,840
And I want you to help me out.

65
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,660
Will you go shopping for me?

66
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,280
Yeah, no problem!

67
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,480
Wait a minute!
Do you even know what to get?

68
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,950
Potato chips and a Okamoto Natsuki photo spread!

69
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:17,820
No!!

70
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:20,850
Listen closely. We need ground pork and radishes...

71
00:03:20,850 --> 00:03:23,000
H-Hold on a second.
I need to take a mome.

72
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,640
You mean "memo," not "mome." I guess he is still just a kid.

73
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,100
Um...

74
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:32,280
Huh? You're left-handed?

75
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:37,280
Oh! It was this hand!

76
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,530
Come on now...
First, ground pork.

77
00:03:39,530 --> 00:03:40,860
Ground...

78
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,640
What letter does "ground" start with?

79
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,579
It's okay.
I'll write the list.

80
00:03:46,579 --> 00:03:50,480
Radishes... Soy sauce...

81
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:52,120
What is it?

82
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,579
Your writing looks like a worm.

83
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,579
• Ground pork
• Radishes
• Soy sauce

84
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,100
Thanks for helping out, Shin-chan!

85
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,779
Hello!

86
00:04:19,779 --> 00:04:21,040
Welcome!

87
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,740
Running an errand?
What a big boy!

88
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:25,240
May I have some
ground pork please?

89
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,700
We don't sell pork here.

90
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,740
May I have some radishes then?

91
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,580
We don't sell radish here either.

92
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:33,880
May I have some soy sauce then?

93
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,540
We don't sell soy sauce either.

