554
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:53,420
Uh, may I have two or three?

555
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:56,690
Didn't you mother tell you how many grams?

556
00:04:57,220 --> 00:04:59,220
How many grams...

557
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,400
Oh!

558
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,860
You remembered?
So how many grams?

559
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,730
She didn't tell me.

560
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,560
This isn't going to work out...

561
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:14,330
Why don't we call your house and ask your mom?

562
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,830
Okay.

563
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,710
What's your telephone number?

564
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,060
Everything's all set.

565
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:35,860
All that's left is the radishes and ground pork.

566
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,060
Welcome home!

567
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:40,200
It's "I'm home,"
not "welcome home."

568
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,780
Wh-What's wrong?

569
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,370
What's our phone number?

570
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:53,330
O-Our phone number?

571
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:59,020
Shinnosuke, I'm going to do the shopping.

572
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:00,680
Watch over house while I'm gone.

573
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,160
You should've just
gone to begin with.

574
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,260
I don't want to hear it!

575
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:10,700
Don't touch the food I prepared for the important client!

576
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,720
Mom!

577
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:16,040
If some guy you don't know comes up to you, don't go with him.

578
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,690
Shut! Your! Mouth!

579
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,440
Help me! Help me!

580
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:28,400
Quiet! No one's going turtle come save you!

581
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:31,740
You're wrong! I know that Action Kamen will come and save me!

582
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:32,940
Turtle, turtle, turtle!

583
00:06:32,940 --> 00:06:37,720
Action Kamen? Too bad I, Black Turtle, already took care of him.

584
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:39,870
Who's there?!

585
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:41,320
They call me...

586
00:06:42,659 --> 00:06:44,050
Action Mask!

587
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:46,920
Action Kick!

588
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:50,090
Action Beam!

589
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:52,320
Turtle!

590
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,510
Thank you, Action Kamen!

591
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:04,420
I'm home.

592
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:07,570
Action Beam!

593
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,520
Are you done?

594
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,540
Yeah.

595
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:19,640
Wow, this looks delicious!

596
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:21,380
Hey, where's Mommy at?

597
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,760
She left us...

598
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,800
What?!

599
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,080
...to get some pork.

600
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,020
Oh, she went shopping.

601
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:31,630
Hey, Mom's gonna
whip your behind!

602
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:36,720
Oh, don't worry. My client had to cancel the dinner.

603
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:39,850
So there's no reason to wait. Let's go ahead and eat.

604
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,810
Okay.

605
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,920
Isn't this tasty, Shinnosuke?

606
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,500
Yeah, it is.

607
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:51,130
So what did you do today, Shinnosuke?

608
00:07:51,130 --> 00:07:52,920
I went shopping.

609
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,659
Wow, you're so grown up!

610
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,120
I am so grown up!

611
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:04,700
Wait for me!
Darling! Shin-chan!

