00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,010
Oh!

619
00:08:10,010 --> 00:08:15,720
Mommy's Mornings Are Busy

620
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:14,720
Mommy's mornings are busy!

621
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:42,500
He's only ridden the kindergarten bus three days this month,

622
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:45,500
even though this month has already been paid for.

623
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:49,460
Such a waste.

624
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:54,180
Shinnosuke! It's morning!

625
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,390
How long are
you going to sleep for?

626
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:59,850
Come on, get up.
You're going to be late again.

627
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:03,310
What are we going to do if you don't get on the bus?

628
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,340
Hey, Shinnosuke!

629
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:15,180
All right then...

630
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,290
Hey, get up!

631
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,250
Huh?

632
00:09:26,250 --> 00:09:28,780
Shinnosuke's disappeared!

633
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:31,080
Could he have been spirited away?

634
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:41,140
You're not supposed to sleep in there, Shinnosuke!

635
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,100
I'm sleepy.

636
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:48,680
Of course you are.
You should've gone to bed earlier.

637
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:52,020
I knew that you wouldn't be able to get up when you stayed up that late.

638
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:54,490
It's your own fault.

639
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:57,300
You're crushing me.

640
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:03,740
Hey, don't sleep in there!

641
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:10,040
C'mon, get your clothes out yourself and change into them.

642
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,460
Okay.

643
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:16,940
Hurry up and change.

644
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:21,180
Don't tell me...

645
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:25,850
No more sleeping!

646
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,350
Yeah, just like that.
Hurry up now.

647
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:32,420
Underwear... Underwear...

648
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:38,030
Pants... Pants...

649
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,490
That's not right.

650
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:44,950
All done.

651
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:47,580
After getting dressed, make sure everything's in your bag.

652
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:48,820
Okay.

653
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:52,000
Monthly Ikagawa

654
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,170
Monthly Ikagawa

655
00:10:52,170 --> 00:10:52,290
Monthly Ikagawa

656
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:52,420
Monthly Ikagawa

657
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,880
It's in here.

658
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:53,880
Monthly Ikagawa

659
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,840
Why are you taking
something like that?!

660
00:10:56,840 --> 00:11:00,300
That doesn't need to be in there!

661
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:05,410
Okay, pack your tissues and handkerchief.

662
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,270
Done.

663
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,080
Hey, hold on!

664
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:21,160
This isn't a handkerchief!

665
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:26,120
Here, wash your face with some cold water. It'll wake you up.

666
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:30,560
Quickly wash up.

667
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,260
Okay...

668
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,260
I've got a bad feeling...

669
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,260
I knew it!

670
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:49,680
Feel the wrath of my triple punch of anger!

671
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:55,180
Eat your breakfast.

672
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:57,380
It's not beef stew?

673
00:11:57,380 --> 00:12:00,780
That takes too long to make for the morning.

674
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:02,360
Just hurry up and eat.

675
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:06,280
Midori from the kindergarten tells me to eat slowly.

676
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,640
Call her "Yoshinaga-sensei"!

677
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:10,250
Chew well and
quickly eat your food.

678
00:12:10,250 --> 00:12:12,740
If you would have
gotten up earlier,

679
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:15,200
you could've eaten your breakfast more slowly.

680
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,300
I'm finished.

681
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:17,670
But you haven't even started.

682
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:27,220
You changed the soup, didn't you?

683
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,850
Never mind that. Hurry up!

684
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,140
I'll eat this.

685
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:39,730
These are no ordinary bean.

686
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,780
They are just normal beans.

687
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,620
Did you steal them?

688
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:46,340
Why would you think I stole them?!

689
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:47,560
Then you bought them?

690
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,900
Of course I did!

691
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:51,780
Then they aren't just normal beans.

692
00:12:52,660 --> 00:12:55,120
Just hurry up and eat!

693
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:13,680
I'm an idiot for giving him beans.

694
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:17,040
You look depressed, Misae.

695
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,720
Hurry up!

696
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,260
Did you brush your teeth?

697
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:22,840
I did.

698
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,660
Did you go pee?

699
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,120
I did.

700
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:24,840
Did you poop?

701
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,160
I didn't.

702
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,480
Hurry up now.

703
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,540
The bus is here to pick you up.

704
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:32,440
Oh, I don't have my hat...

705
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,100
Hurry and go get it!

706
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,720
Here.

707
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:40,140
If you don't make it
on the bus today,

708
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:42,050
it won't be the only
thing leaving you.

709
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,970
I couldn't find it, so I'll use this.

710
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:49,180
You idiot!

711
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,320
Good morning, sensei!

712
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,420
Good morning!

713
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,540
Good afternoon!

714
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:59,080
You mean "good morning."

715
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:03,530
Okay, Shin-chan.
Why don't you get on the bus?

716
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:07,740
Okay, whatever you say, Midori.

717
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:17,880
What's wrong, Shinnosuke?

718
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,400
I need to poop.

719
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,920
Just keep it in!

720
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,380
A bit came out...

721
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:33,020
Go on without him.

722
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:35,340
I'll bring him in later.

723
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:36,810
Okay...

724
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:50,340
