00:15:15,010 --> 00:15:20,770
Doodling

735
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:19,120
Doodling!

736
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:24,660
Good morning, sensei!

737
00:15:24,660 --> 00:15:26,730
Good morning!

738
00:15:26,730 --> 00:15:28,820
Today, we're going to doodle.

739
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,700
Did everyone bring their crayons?

740
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:32,260
Yes!

741
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:33,560
Okay, then...

742
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,540
Shinnosuke-kun?

743
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:40,720
What's wrong? Are you okay?

744
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:42,680
I've got a nosebleed.

745
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:47,000
If you keep doing that, you're going to have nose like a pig!

746
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:49,460
Have you tried this, sensei?

747
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:52,640
Does it look like I have a pig nose?

748
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:56,430
Calm down, Midori. You shouldn't get so worked up over a kid.

749
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:00,930
Shin-chan! This is the second time I've told you to stop playing around.

750
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,650
I've got a runny nose.

751
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:08,900
I told you to stop!

752
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:12,040
Today, you can draw whatever you like.

753
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:14,520
Animals, flowers — anything is fine!

754
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,380
Okay!

755
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:17,430
What are you going to draw, Shin-chan?

756
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:26,460
Where are you going, Shin-chan?

757
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:29,960
You want me to stay still?

758
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:32,600
Hey, what are you
doing over there?

759
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,520
Drawing what I like.

760
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,430
You don't need to use a model.

761
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:41,040
A drawing is something you use your imagination to come up with on paper.

762
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:41,850
My imagination?

763
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:46,400
Yes! You close your eyes like this and draw whatever you see in your head.

764
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:49,780
Wow! I can see a beautiful flower garden!

765
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:51,820
Now you give it a try!

766
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,430
Yeah, just like that.

767
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:56,780
Oh!

768
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:59,440
Good! Now do you see anything?

769
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:02,360
I can't see anything except darkness.

770
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:10,170
Okay, let's see what kind of things you are all drawing!

771
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,700
You're drawing a flower, right, Nene-chan?

772
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,130
That's right, Yoshinaga-sensei!

773
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:15,589
It's a beautiful flower.

774
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:18,440
I really tried hard to draw it.

775
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,859
Me too, sensei.

776
00:17:20,859 --> 00:17:22,560
I'm a beautiful flower.

777
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:24,520
Quit with your nonsense.

778
00:17:24,819 --> 00:17:26,180
Nonsense?

779
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:29,480
Stop sticking crayons up your nose!

780
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,730
Okay.

781
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:33,840
Masao-kun, what are you drawing?

782
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:36,220
Let me see it.

783
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:38,870
