You haven't even
drawn anything yet.

876
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,800
But I thought I could whatever.

877
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:20,700
Anything is fine.
Like an airplane or a bicycle.

878
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:22,490
I'll draw an airplane!

879
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,240
What's wrong, Shin-chan?

880
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,900
What does an
airplane look like again?

881
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:38,480
Like this! In the middle, you have the body that looks like a log...

882
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,090
I see...

883
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:43,420
Then it has two big wings and three small ones.

884
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:44,510
I see...

885
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:46,200
And then it flies!

886
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:50,470
Varooom! Varooom!
 Woooosh! Woooosh!

887
00:20:50,470 --> 00:20:51,600
Did you get that?

888
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:52,430
Yes!

889
00:20:59,040 --> 00:21:00,860
What does it look like again?

890
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:03,660
Forget it.
I'll help you out a bit.

891
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,910
Thanks!

