905
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:33,060
Matsuzaka-sensei!

906
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:36,880
But that's not even the average level for my Rose Class.

907
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:40,040
Only in your class would that be considered excellent.

908
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:45,990
